Job Description
My client is a leading multinational power generation company based in the Middle East with projects worldwide.
They are looking for a high caliber Mechanical Engineer with strong experience in detailed engineering design to be responsible for supporting and developing a team of experienced Engineers, Junior Engineers and Designers and will be involved in detailed design and construction support for several large new build Power projects in the Middle East.
There will be an attractive remuneration package on a fixed term contract basis for the right candidate.
The ideal candidate is:
A Mechanical Design Engineer10 Years + Experience on Power projects - CCGT experience is an advantageDegree Qualified - RelevantDetailed Engineering Design experience Flexible with/ able to work in the Middle East
If you have sufficient experience in Mechanical Engineering, with strong experience in the Power sector, with the hope of establishing yourself in a reputable international organization and taking on a great new challenge, then this could be the perfect opportunity for you!
Qualifications
Bachelors Degree or equivalent
